---
title: Blog
description:
heading:
  My two cents on web development.
paragraph:
  Here you will find my thoughts, opinions, findings, and neat tricks I have discovered over my years in web development. I reserve the right to change my mind about anything I say at any time.
---

{% extends 'page.njk' %}

{% block body %}

  <section class="gradient-purple text-white py-8 lg:py-16">
    <div class="container max-w-screen-md mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold leading-none">
        {{ heading }}
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-indigo-100">{{ paragraph }}</p>
      <a class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center border px-2 py-2 rounded" href="/feed.xml">
        <span class="font-medium tracking-tight leading-none">
          RSS Feed
        </span>
        <span class="ml-2 w-6 h-6 block">
          {% include 'icons/rss.svg' %}
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <span class="w-full h-12 block gradient-purple text-gray-100">
    {% include 'icons/waves.svg' %}
  </span>

  <section class="container max-w-screen-md mt-16">
    {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
      <article class="sm:flex pt-8 mt-8 {{ 'border-t' if not loop.first }}">
        <div class="sm:w-1/4">
          <p>{{ post.data.date | date }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-2 sm:mt-0 sm:w-3/4">
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold leading-none">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
          </a>
          <p class="text-base mt-4">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
          <a
            href="{{ post.url }}"
            class="inline-flex items-center mt-6 text-indigo-500 font-bold"
          >
            <span class="leading-none">
              Read More
            </span>
            <span class="w-4 ml-1">
              {% include 'icons/arrow.svg' %}
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>

{% endblock %}
